# Undead Burg Skip (LUB)

The skip allows to quickly access the Lower [Undead Burg](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/undead-burg) from Undead Burg without acquiring any key beforehand.

There are tons of ways to perform this jump; you will find more revealing ones on this page.

For more LUB skip you can watch here : [LUB Skips](https://soulsspeedruns.com/darksouls/lower-undead-burg-skip)

